#Tallying up the points
Holiday_tally = sum(Holiday)

Lillard_tally = sum(Lillard)
Harden_tally = sum(Harden)
Curry_tally = sum(Curry)

#X-Axis (Labels)
players_label = ['Jrue Holiday', 'Russell Westbrook', 'Damian Lillard', 'James Harden', 'Stephen Curry']
#Converting the X-Axis into an array
players_label_arr = np.array(players_label)

#Y-Axis (Values for the labels)
tally = [Holiday_tally, Westbrook_tally, Lillard_tally, Harden_tally, Curry_tally]

#Plotting the Bar
plt.bar(players_label_arr, tally)

#Labelling X and Y axes
plt.xlabel('Player Names', fontsize = 20, color='DarkBlue')
plt.ylabel('Total Points', fontsize = 20, color='DarkBlue')

#The Title
plt.title("WC Point Guard - Final Rankings", fontsize=35, color="DarkBlue", fontname="Console")

#Displaying the Bar
plt.show()
